data.description: BACK ON MARKET at no fault of Seller.  Revised Rent Rolls in TD.  Ready to close!   This 4 Plex has 4, 2 bedrooms, 1 bath units. The entire building has been totally remodeled from the studs out, including the Sewer line was replaced to the Mainline.  All the units are very spacious and are bright with new windows in every room and painted with the New Updated Gray and White colors.  Central Heat and Air, Washer and Dryer in Basement for the Convenience of each renter, Complex has an Emergency Fire Hydrant System, The Building is Accessible, and has one unit downstairs Accessible.  Each unit has its own Water Heater.  All tenants pay their own Electric bills and the Water/trash/sewer bill are split and shared. Owner pays for Electric bill for common areas. The Location is close to downtown, shopping, Plaza District, Bricktown and more.  Please do not disturb the tenants, the complex is 100% full.  Is under contract and taking backups.  All inspections have been done.
